                              Subject : PLAYING

      BTU     How BTUs are generated
 Selector *   Selectors you can use in Empire conditionals
    Sheep     Ovis aries
   Syntax *   The Empire command syntax
     Time     ETUs, BTUs and ETL

  apropos *   Searches info pages for information on a topic
      bye *   Log out of Empire
  country     Find out country status
  execute     Execute a batch file
     help *   Provide information on various topics
     info *   Provide information on various topics
     list     List commands which are currently legal
  players     List players currently connected to the game
     pray *   Interacting with the Deity
     quit *   Log out of Empire
  version     Display parameters of this world

For  info  on  a particular topic, type "info <topic>" where <topic> is one of
the topics listed above.  Topics marked by * are the most important and should
be read by new players.

